  dom_head_meta("description", "Why the source never dies: coupling asymmetry creates sigma surplus. In Z/210Z, the coupling sum inside the HYDOR boundary exceeds outside by exactly sigma=1. Position SUN=54 is D,K-null: it MUST radiate. 51+105+54=210.");
